products.name: Toy Car
products.description: Toy cars make great gifts, and what better than to give them a traditional wooden toy car that is this cute? It’s a great size for popping in a bag – or even a pocket – for play dates and as emergency toy supplies for days out. A real hand made toy with tons of style and play value for all kinds of imagination-fueled adventures, and a great hand made gift for babies and toddlers.
